clamped_clamped_trial_functions.png.description: Two graphs showing clamped-clamped trial functions - left graph shows polynomial functions with boundary conditions phi=0 and phi_x=0 at both ends, right graph shows trigonometric functions with same boundary conditions

clamped_free_trial_functions.png.description: Graph showing clamped-free polynomial trial functions with boundary condition phi=0 and phi_x=0 at left end

clamped_supported_trial_functions.png.description: Graph showing clamped-supported polynomial trial functions with boundary conditions phi=0 and phi_x=0 at left end, phi=0 at right end

supported_supported_trial_functions.png.description: Two graphs showing supported-supported trial functions - left graph shows polynomial functions with boundary condition phi=0 at both ends, right graph shows trigonometric functions with same boundary conditions

rectangular_plate_coordinate_system.png.description: Rectangular plate diagram showing coordinate system with x and y axes, dimensions a and b labeled, representing the problem setup for aluminum plate analysis

cccc_plate_bending_response_contours.png.description: Eight contour plots showing displacement and moment distributions for CCCC plate with uniformly distributed and concentrated loads - includes w, Mxx, Myy, and Mxy for both load cases

cccc_plate_vibration_mode_shapes.png.description: Four mode shape contour plots showing first four free vibration modes of CCCC plate with aspect ratio variations
